create cluster 
===================
    $ eksctl create cluster  (default command )

--> it creates two m5.large large nodes by default for data nodes. Instead of t3.micro 

    control plane -- Always aws take care  (per hour 10rs only for control plane)
	
	data plane (worker nodes )  -- two m5.large worker nodes  (by default it will create m5.large but to reduce cost creating in t3.micro)
	
	customize command --> to reduse the node cost 
	
	$ eksctl create cluster --name ramcluster --nodegroup-name ramng --node-type t3.micro --nodes 4 --managed

